<header class="entry-header">
<h1 class="entry-title">The 12 Best Cat Beds</h1>
</header>
<div class="entry-content">
<div class="disc">
<h3>Our Review Process</h3>
Our reviews are based on extensive research and, when possible, hands-on testing. Each time you make a purchase through one of our independently-chosen links, well receive a percentage of the proceeds. Read more about how were supported <a href="https://allaboutcats.com/affiliate-disclosure" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">here.</a>
</div>
<p>At the end of a long day, all you want to do is curl up in a nice, comfy bed. Doesnt your cat deserve the same? The trouble many cat owners run into is that their cats tend to ignore the special (often expensive) items we buy them in favor of the box they came in.</p>
<p>So, how do you choose a bed your cat will actually like?</p>
<p>Theres no one-size-fits-all answer but there are certain features and characteristics you should look for in a cat bed. The right bed will provide your cat not only with a comfortable surface for <a href="https://allaboutcats.com/why-do-cats-sleep-so-much" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sleep</a>, but it can become a place for him to call his own. Thats all anyone really wants.</p>
<h2>At A Glance: Our Top Picks For Best Cat Beds</h2>
